com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.framework.extensions

Interface ISCUILocale

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SCUILocale

    public interface ISCUILocale
    This is a locale interface provided by the framework. An implementation of this class provided by the application will be passed around.
    ISCUILocale stores the locale specific information about a region. hyadav
